<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, September 7 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 682.08 points Tuesday, up 0.39 percent from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 92,763 shares changed hands
in 5937 deals, and the turnover was 2,075,134 dinars (1,886,485
U.S. dollars). 
</P>
</TEXT>
