Council, praised the 10 armed police officers.
</P>
<P>
The armed police are loyal to the Party, the people and their
duty, and have made important contributions to the national
security and social stability.
</P>
<P>
Official figures show that over the past three years, 76 armed
policemen died in line of duty or in fighting disasters and were
named revolutionary martyrs.
</P>
<P>
In 1998, the armed police selected the first group of Top 10
Loyal Guards. So far, 20 police officers have won the title.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
