<HEADLINE> Greek PM Postpones Visit to China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 9 (Xinhua) -- Greek Prime Minister
Constantine Simitis has decided to postpone his official visit to
China originally scheduled between September 15 and 21, due to the
earthquake at home.
</P>
<P>
This was released by Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman Sun
Yuxi this afternoon. 
</P>
</TEXT>
