Ethnic Games, lit a torch from the Vessel, handing it down to
Beijing mayor and chairman of the Ethnic Games organising
committee Liu Qi. The torch was then relayed to the Beijing
Workers' Stadium, the main arena of the Games.
</P>
<P>
