<P>
Business World:
</P>
<P>
-- The explosion of violence in East Timor sent the Philippine
peso beyond 40 pesos against one U.S. dollar level Wednesday, but
government economic officials and local currency traders said the
local currency's decline should be temporary.
</P>
<P>
Manila Bulletin:
</P>
<P>
-- Jacqueline Ejercito, the only daughter of Philippine
President Joseph Estrada, and Manuel Lopez Jr. exchanged "I do's"
in a lavish wedding ceremony at 7 p.m. Wednesday night at Manila
Metropolitan Cathedral, witnessed by some 1,000 guests. 
</P>
