some in critical condition.
</P>
<P>
The Taliban militia have raided Taloqan, provincial capital of
Takhar, with heavy aerial bombardments over the last four days,
confirmed independent sources.
</P>
<P>
The militia have since late July been in a fresh round of
offensive against their opponents controlling the northeastern
provinces of Afghanistan. 
